      ],
      "details": {}
    },
    {
      "review_id": "rJe1e3jj3X",
      "rebuttal_id": "BJlit-i1Rm",
      "sentence_index": 7,
      "text": "So the measurement we proposed is a best-effort attempt that can hopefully give us some insights into this problem.",
